Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔准機會 TAKE A BRAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論這片廣闊風景向何處延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RIDE ON THE NEW CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時黑白顛倒  也會發生爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將危機和悲劇統統轉化為堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能夠無功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使跌倒了百萬回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅散密布的烏雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會 OPEN THE WORLDS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我們的終點各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要懷抱無數個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無數次 OPEN THE WORLDS
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,EDJP PEARLY×PARTY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.24,Default_Top,NTP,0,0,0,,気になってるって　パンクしちゃうほど(妖精!)
